Description: Smart AP+STA WiFi hotspot manager for Linux
 apsta helps run a WiFi hotspot while maintaining an upstream WiFi
 client connection where hardware supports AP+STA operation.
 .
 It includes:
	- apsta CLI for detect/start/stop/status/config
	- apsta-gtk GUI for GTK4/Libadwaita desktops
	- systemd service and sleep hook files for persistence flows
